data.description: WELCOME HOME to this spacious and comfortable single level 4 bedroom, 2 bathroom home in a rare subdivision with NO HOA dues!  The 12 by 12 bonus room can be used as a 5th bedroom, office, exercise room or den.   Well maintained home with a new HVAC system in 2021, new architectural shingle roof in 2022 and a new water heater in 2020.  Bright, airy and open floorplan, split bedroom design, vaulted ceilings in the Great Room and kitchen, plant shelves for decorating and large covered front porch.  The kitchen features newer appliances, a breakfast bar, built-in microwave plus a corner pantry and a dining area with a glass slider door to the spacious back patio.  Master bedroom with en-suite bathroom and convenient walk-in closet.  Super-sized and fully fenced back yard, full automatic sprinklers and lots of space for gardening and flowers.  This home is vacant, easy to show and available for a quick closing.  MOVE RIGHT IN!
